dc_description_s: These data layers represent zoning for Monroe County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, NMonroe_Zoning_2018.gdbN. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are NMonroe_Airport_2018N, NMonroe_Farmland_Preservation_Program_2018N, and NMonroe_General_2018N. [Zoning codes for parcels under Monroe County zoning.]
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
dc_subject_sm: Zoning - Maps, City Planning, County Ordinances
